&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;As an individual contributor, the Manufacturing Counsel will operate as a trusted legal advisor, applying sound judgment, practical risk assessment, and a collaborative, solutions‑oriented approach in a fast‑paced, scaling manufacturing environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reporting relationship:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Senior Director, Senior Corporate Counsel (Princeton, NJ), with dotted-line reporting relationship to the Vice President of Manufacturing (Sanford, NC).&lt;/p&gt;
